'''The Elite''' were the highest ranking members of the four main [[Yuuzhan Vong castes|castes]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. They were the leaders of the [[Warrior caste|Warrior]], [[Intendant caste|Intendant]], [[Shaper caste|Shaper]], and [[Priest caste]]s, and made up the court of the [[Supreme Overlord]] of the Yuuzhan Vong.

